{{TechInfoDepot|Sitecom_WL-105b}}
The DD-WRT supported devices table states the FCC ID for this device is MXF-A910910AB. This FCC ID has a BCM4301+BCM2051 card and an Atheros AR5000 card for 802.11a. This access point appears to use a BCM4306+BCM2050 card [https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=4341].
